    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All thirteen credibility factors have been reviewed against MRL 5 requirements. The assessment team concludes that the CFD hemolysis model demonstrates sufficient fidelity for regulatory submission purposes. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was conducted and results are considered supportive of the hemolysis predictions within the stated operating envelope. The credibility evidence package is accepted for submission to the regulatory dossier.",
